        <h3>Business Context Summary</h3>
        <p>
          This document defines the requirements for a comprehensive financ=
ial projection engine tailored for a
          multi-market F&amp;B Dark Kitchen business. The system is designe=
d as a "Finance-First" planning tool,
          prioritizing high-level driver-based modeling over granular opera=
tional transaction logging. It serves as the
          single source of truth for strategic planning, fundraising, and r=
ecurring financial forecasting.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Core Design Rule:</strong> "Any detail that does not chan=
ge a financial decision in the next 6=E2=80=9318
          months does not belong in core v1."
        </p>
