    <div class=3D"layer-spine" style=3D"padding-left: 15px">
      <h3>Functional Requirements</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Req ID</th>
            <th>Priority</th>
            <th>Description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>PRD-PS-001</td>
            <td class=3D"priority-p0">P0</td>
            <td>
              <strong>Company Entity:</strong> System must support multi-te=
nancy where each Company has a distinct base
              currency, fiscal year definition, and isolated data namespace=
.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PRD-PS-002</td>
            <td class=3D"priority-p0">P0</td>
            <td>
              <strong>Planning Periods:</strong> System must generate and m=
anage Planning Periods (Month, Quarter, Year)
              dynamically based on the Company's Fiscal Year start date.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PRD-PS-003</td>
            <td class=3D"priority-p0">P0</td>
            <td>
              <strong>Scenario Management:</strong> Users must be able to c=
reate named Scenarios (e.g., "Base",
              "Upside") that inherit or override assumptions.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PRD-PS-004</td>
            <td class=3D"priority-p0">P0</td>
            <td>
              <strong>Assumption Sets:</strong> Assumptions must be grouped=
 into versioned Sets. A Scenario maps to
              exactly one active Assumption Set per Planning Period range.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PRD-PS-005</td>
