      </li>
      <li><strong>Audit Fields:</strong> `created_by`, `updated_by`, `creat=
ed_at`, `updated_at` on all tables.</li>
      <li><strong>Total Tables:</strong> 73 (62 Core + 11 Extension).</li>
    </ul>

