          <td>Unit Tests</td>
          <td>Formula accuracy, individual functions</td>
          <td>Jest/PyTest</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Integration Tests</td>
          <td>Data flow between Layers A-J</td>
          <td>Supertest</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Projection Accuracy</td>
          <td>Verified inputs =3D Verified outputs</td>
          <td>Custom Engine Harness</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Monte Carlo Validation</td>
          <td>Distribution shape verification</td>
          <td>Statistical checks</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Security Tests</td>
          <td>Penetration, RBAC enforcement</td>
          <td>OWASP ZAP</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 id=3D"section-23" class=3D"section-header">23. Phased Delivery Road=
map Summary</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Phase</th>
          <th>Weeks</th>
          <th>Deliverable</th>
          <th>Key Gate Criteria</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 0</td>
          <td>1-4</td>
          <td>Infrastructure</td>
          <td>CI/CD, Auth, Schema Init</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 1</td>
          <td>5-12</td>
          <td>Planning Spine MVP</td>
          <td>Scenarios, Markets, Products defined</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 2</td>
          <td>13-24</td>
          <td>Driver &amp; Projection Engine</td>
          <td>P&amp;L, Cash Flow computing correctly</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 3</td>
          <td>25-36</td>
          <td>Scenario &amp; Intelligence</td>
          <td>KPIs, Comparison, Explainability</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 4</td>
          <td>37-48</td>
          <td>Risk, Sim &amp; Capital</td>
          <td>Monte Carlo, Funding logic live</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 5</td>
          <td>49-60</td>
          <td>Governance &amp; Portfolio</td>
          <td>Approval workflow, Portfolio Opt</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Phase 6</td>
          <td>61+</td>
          <td>Operational Extensions</td>
          <td>Optional modules integration</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 id=3D"section-24" class=3D"section-header">24. Glossary</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Planning Spine:</strong> The core hierarchy of Company &gt;=
 Scenario &gt; Assumption Set &gt; Planning Period.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Planning Grain:</strong> The level of detail for a projec=
tion (e.g., Market vs Kitchen level).</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Driver-Based Modeling:</strong> Using operational inputs (O=
rders, AOV) to derive financial outputs
        (Revenue).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>CM (Contribution Margin):</strong> Revenue minus variable c=
osts. CM0 (Gross), CM1 (post-food), CM2
        (post-labor/delivery).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Decision Memory:</strong> System feature that logs strategi=
c choices and rationale for future analysis.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Dark Kitchen:</strong> A delivery-only food production un=
it with no dine-in facility.</li>
    </ul>
